00:21:41.480 --> 00:21:42.540
D'accord, d'accord.

00:21:43.750 --> 00:21:44.390
je vous promets

00:21:44.390 --> 00:21:45.590
♪ Il y a des érudits raffinés
en robes blanches ♪

00:21:45.590 --> 00:21:47.850
